âœ… 6. Update a Record
Letâ€™s say you want to update the price of "The Hobbit" to 350.00:

UPDATE Books
SET price = 350.00
WHERE title = 'The Hobbit';
ğŸ“Œ This updates only the record where the title is "The Hobbit".

âœ… 7. Delete a Record
Now, letâ€™s delete the book "Atomic Habits":

DELETE FROM Books
WHERE title = 'Atomic Habits';
ğŸ“Œ This removes the record matching the given title.

âœ… 8. View Updated Table
